doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Desta Collection - Solusi Produksi Busana Muslim, Seragam, dan Pakaian Dinas

        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Bootstrap Icons
        link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.5.0/font/bootstrap-icons.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // SimpleLightbox plugin CSS
        link(href='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/SimpleLightbox/2.1.0/simpleLightbox.min.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body#page-top

        // Navigation
        nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-light.fixed-top.py-3
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='#page-top') 
                    h4.mb-0 Destia Collection
                button.navbar-toggler.navbar-toggler-right(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarResponsive', aria-controls='navbarResponsive', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                #navbarResponsive.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.my-2.my-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#about') Tentang
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#services') Layanan
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#portfolio') Portfolio
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#contact') Kontak

        // Masthead
        header.masthead
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.h-100
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.h-100.align-items-center.justify-content-center.text-center
                    .col-lg-8.align-self-end
                        h1.text-white.font-weight-bold Mau bikin baju Dinas? Seragam Kerja? atau Busana Muslim?
                        hr.divider
                    .col-lg-8.align-self-baseline
                        p.text-white-75.mb-5
                            | Pesan saja di Destia collection, solusi terbaik untuk produksi segala macam kebutuhan busana Anda dengan cepat dan hemat.
                        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href='#about') Selengkapnya

        // About
        section#about.page-section.bg-primary
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5.justify-content-center
                    .col-lg-8.text-center
                        h2.text-white.mt-0 Tentang Kami 
                        hr.divider.divider-light
                        p.text-white-75.mb-4
                            | Berlokasi di Bandung, Destia Collection hadir sebagai vendor konveksi yang dapat meningkatkan nilai bisnis Anda melalui hasil produksi pakaian yang berkualitas. Destia Collection juga menyediakan bermacam koleksi busana terbaik sesuai kebutuhan Anda.
                        a.btn.btn-light.btn-xl(href='#services') Layanan Kami

        // Services
        section#services.page-section
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                h2.text-center.mt-0 Apa yang akan Anda dapatkan?
                hr.divider
                .row.gx-4.gx-lg-5
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-stack.text-primary(style="font-size: 42pt")
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Produksi Masal
                            p.text-muted.mb-0 Anda bebas menentukan kuantitas produksi sesuka hati
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-stopwatch.text-primary(style="font-size: 42pt")
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Proses Cepat
                            p.text-muted.mb-0 Tidak perlu menunggu lama untuk melihat hasil produksi sampai di tangan Anda
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-shield-fill-check.text-primary(style="font-size: 42pt")
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Kualitas Terjamin
                            p.text-muted.mb-0 Semua produksi dibuat oleh tangan-tangan terampil yang handal dalam bidangnya
                    .col-lg-3.col-md-6.text-center
                        .mt-5
                            .mb-2
                                i.bi-cash-coin.text-primary(style="font-size: 42pt")
                            h3.h4.mb-2 Hemat Biaya
                            p.text-muted.mb-0 Tidak perlu khawatir dengan harga, pasti dijamin murah dan berkualitas

        // Portfolio
        #portfolio
            .container-fluid.p-0
                .row.g-0
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                        a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/gamis-rayon-full.jpg', title='Bahan Rayon Rp 105.000')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/gamis-rayon.jpg', alt='...')
                            .portfolio-box-caption
                                .project-category.text-white-50
                                    | Busana Muslim
                                .project-name
                                    | Gamis Wanita Bahan Rayon
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                        a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/pdh.jpg', title='PDH + Atribut Rp 210.000')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/pdh.jpg', alt='...')
                            .portfolio-box-caption
                                .project-category.text-white-50
                                    | Pakaian Dinas
                                .project-name
                                    | PDH + Atribut
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                        a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/gamis-rayon-full-premium.jpg', title='Bahan Rayon Premium Rp 110.000')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/gamis-rayon-premium.jpg', alt='...')
                            .portfolio-box-caption
                                .project-category.text-white-50
                                    | Busana Muslim
                                .project-name
                                    | Gamis Wanita Bahan Rayon Premium
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                        a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/safari.jpg', title='Safari + Atribut Rp 280.000')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/safari.jpg', alt='...')
                            .portfolio-box-caption
                                .project-category.text-white-50
                                    | Pakaian Safari
                                .project-name
                                    | Safari + Atribut
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                        a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/pdl.jpg', title='PDL + Atribut Rp 225.000')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/pdl.jpg', alt='...')
                            .portfolio-box-caption
                                .project-category.text-white-50
                                    | Pakaian Dinas
                                .project-name
                                    | PDL + Atribut
                    .col-lg-4.col-sm-6
                        a.portfolio-box(href='assets/img/portfolio/fullsize/pabrik.jpg', title='Seragam Pabrik')
                            img.img-fluid(src='assets/img/portfolio/thumbnails/pabrik.jpg', alt='...')
                            .portfolio-box-caption.p-3
                                .project-category.text-white-50
                                    | Seragam
                                .project-name
                                    | Seragam Pabrik

        // Call to action
        section.page-section.bg-dark.text-white
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5.text-center
                h2.mb-4 Online Store
                p.text-center Bisa dipesan secara online dari marketplace favorit kamu
                .row.justify-content-evenly
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6
                        .card.text-center.py-4.my-4
                            img.card-img-top.mx-auto.my-4(src="../assets/img/logo-marketplace/tokopedia-logo.png", alt="tokopedia logo" style="width: 150px;")
                            .card-body
                                a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href="https://tokopedia.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Order via Tokopedia
                    .col-lg-4.col-md-6
                            .card.text-center.py-4.my-4
                                img.card-img-top.mx-auto.my-4(src="../assets/img/logo-marketplace/shopee-logo.png", alt="tokopedia logo" style="width: 150px;")
                                .card-body
                                    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-xl(href="https://shopee.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer") Order via Shopee

        // Contact
        section#contact.page-section
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                .row
                    .col-lg-5.order-lg-1.contact
                        h3 Destia Collection
                    .col-lg-4.order-lg-3.contact
                        h5 Contact Info
                        address.mt-4 Welcome to Destia Collection! Kami siap mendukung produk lokal dan industri kreatif di Indonesia.
                        | Alamat: <br>
                        | Jl. Bojong Cipandan Kidul RT 04/20 <br>
                        | Soreang, Bandung <br> <br>
                        | Whatsapp: +62 8122 033 123 <br>
                        | Email: support@destiacollection.com
                    .col-lg-3.order-lg-2
                        h5 Sitemap
                        ul.nav.flex-column.mt-4
                            li.nav-item.mb-3
                                a.nav-link.text-muted.p-0(href="#") Home
                            li.nav-item.mb-3
                                a.nav-link.text-muted.p-0(href="#") About
                            li.nav-item.mb-3
                                a.nav-link.text-muted.p-0(href="#") Services
                            li.nav-item.mb-3
                                a.nav-link.text-muted.p-0(href="#") Portfolio
                            li.nav-item.mb-3
                                a.nav-link.text-muted.p-0(href="#") Contact

        // Footer
        footer.bg-light.py-5
            .container.px-4.px-lg-5
                .row.footrow.align-items-center
                    .col-auto.me-auto
                        .small.text-muted
                            | Copyright &copy; 2021 - Destia Collection
                    .col-auto
                        ul.list-unstyled.d-flex.mb-0
                            li.mx-3
                                a.link-dark(href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer")
                                    i.bi-instagram
                            li.mx-3
                                a.link-dark(href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer")
                                    i.bi-facebook
                            li.mx-3
                                a.link-dark(href="https://twitter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer")
                                    i.bi-twitter
                            li.mx-3
                                a.link-dark(href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer")
                                    i.bi-youtube

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // SimpleLightbox plugin JS
        script(src='https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/SimpleLightbox/2.1.0/simpleLightbox.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')
